Subject:  Re: [T2] Today i started the bus, and it didn't like me at all

New exhaust gaskets, between the head and exhaust manifold will smoke on 
first startup.  I'm figuring you didn't let it run long because the leaky 
oil cooler. It might even be oil dripping on the exhaust from the leaky oil 
cooler. Also the smoke from the exhaust usually seems to dissipate within a 
few minutes after a fresh engine rebuild.
Just some ideas to consider

Alex Wisniewski
Nashville, TN
'77 Riviera camper


